xxl.core.functions

Interface MetaDataFunction<P,R,M>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the function's parameters.
    R - the return type of the function.
    M - the type of the meta data provided by this function.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Function<P,R>, MetaDataProvider<M>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMetaDataFunction, CMDFunction, FunctionMetaDataFunction

    public interface MetaDataFunction<P,R,M>
extends Function<P,R>, MetaDataProvider<M>
    A marker interface for functions providing metadata.
